Hi, nice to meet you!

I'm Devair Junior.

Resident in Alfenas-MG, I am a Front-end developer passionate about developing web applications that are easily accessible to users.

A B O U T . M E

Front-end developer with experience in React.js, Next.js, Redux, JavaScript, TypeScript, Styled Components, Material UI and consumption of REST APIs. Passionate about developing reusable components. I also have experience in projects managed by Agile Methodologies. Graduated in Biotechnology and passionate about the world of programming since 2015.
